{"tid":356842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭 融 被 老 外 男 友 改 變","createTime":"2017-08-12T12:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T03:20:51.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"543e665b0f3f00f1dfb6f07b652aa84ac8968c15","tid":356842,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"鄭融、韋雄同監製周錫漢噚日喺商台宣傳新歌《I'll be with You》，其間鄭融提到外籍男友令佢改變。<br />\n問鄭融錄歌嗰陣係咪諗住男友？佢話：「反而好似唱畀自己聽咁，因為首歌入面，I'll be with you出現咗十幾次，當我聽到呢首歌嘅demo嗰陣，人生好低落，嗰時冇拍拖，好似所有嘢都要自己面對。好感激自己陪住自己，覺得呢幾年自己成長咗唔少。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170810/large/10ec2p8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170810%2Flarge%2F10ec2p8a.jpg&h=eda82871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cab000310b85f74715d914ba22590e0af518eb3","tid":356842,"uid":23833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"又矮又老腳又短又粗<br />\n<br />\n真係得鬼佬會埋單"},{"pid":"e1cc092290d4ce4db837453238f220906fe7328e","tid":356842,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"何方妖怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5551c60234bd3aa748ee76e56dca301c268c2d2","tid":356842,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"嘩邊位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd71dcbefeb83b6bc1cfb2c2d0155b49a8e9a2d","tid":356842,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"西部大開發?"},{"pid":"a98f2bcdbbf87543305738f39e4b40a2dace1aa4","tid":356842,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:16:23.000Z","msg":"個鬼妹都係貪佢似賓妹遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid